# 📚 E-commerce Bookstore

An online bookstore web application where users can register, log in, view books, add them to cart, and place orders — built using **React** for the frontend and **Flask + PostgreSQL** for the backend.

---

## 🚀 Features

- 👤 User Registration
- 🔐 Secure Login Handling
- 📖 View All Available Books
- 🛒 Add Books to Cart
- 💳 Checkout & Place Orders
- 🗃️ PostgreSQL for all data storage
- 🔄 React frontend + Flask API backend

---

## 🛠️ Tech Stack

| Layer        | Tech Used        |
|--------------|------------------|
| Frontend     | React.js         |
| Backend      | Flask (Python)   |
| Database     | PostgreSQL       |
| Styling      | CSS              |
| API Bridge   | Flask-CORS       |

---

